qDef.qDef:
=
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Revenue'),
	[Revenue Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Expense'),
	[Expense Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'NOI'),
	[NOI Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Crisis Response'),
	[Crisis Response Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Bonusable NOI'),
	[Bonusable NOI Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded]
    
)))))

=
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Revenue'),
	[Revenue Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Expense'),
	[Expense Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'NOI'),
	[NOI Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Crisis Response'),
	[Crisis Response Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Bonusable NOI'),
	[Bonusable NOI Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded]
    
)))))

=
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Revenue'),
	[Revenue Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded]
	+
	[Revenue Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Expense'),
	[Expense Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded]
	+
	[Expense Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'NOI'),
	[NOI Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded]
    +
    [NOI Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Crisis Response'),
	[Crisis Response Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded]
	+
	[Crisis Response Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Bonusable NOI'),
	[Bonusable NOI Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded]
    +
    [Bonusable NOI Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded]
    
)))))

=IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Revenue'),
	[Revenue Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Expense'),
	[Expense Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'NOI'),
	[NOI Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Crisis Response'),
	[Crisis Response Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Bonusable NOI'),
	[Bonusable NOI Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded]
    
)))))

=IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Revenue'),
	( [Revenue Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded] + [Revenue Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded] ) - [Revenue Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Expense'),
	 [Expense Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded] - ( [Expense Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded] + [Expense Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded] ),    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'NOI'),
	( [NOI Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded] + [NOI Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded] ) - [NOI Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Crisis Response'),
	( [Crisis Response Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded] + [Crisis Response Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded] ) - [Crisis Response Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded],
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Bonusable NOI'),
	( [Bonusable NOI Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded] + [Bonusable NOI Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded] ) - [Bonusable NOI Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded]
    
)))))

=IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Revenue'),
	NUM(( [Revenue Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded] + [Revenue Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded] ) / [Revenue Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded], '##0%'),
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Expense'),
	NUM(( [Expense Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded] + [Expense Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded] ) / [Expense Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded], '##0%'),
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'NOI'),
	NUM(Floor((([NOI Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded] + [NOI Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded]) - [NOI Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded])/Fabs([NOI Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded])+1, .001), '##0.0%'),
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Crisis Response'),
	NUM(( [Crisis Response Actual (YTD) - Nonexcluded] + [Crisis Response Ops Plan (remaining year) - Nonexcluded] ) / [Crisis Response Ops Plan (Current Year) - Nonexcluded], '##0%'),
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Revenue', 'Expense', 'NOI', 'Crisis Response', 'Bonusable NOI'), 'Bonusable NOI'),
	NUM([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded], '##0.0%')
)))))

qFieldDefs: =ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility')

qDef.qDef:
=
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Quality Scores'),
	' ',
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), '% of NOI Target'),
	NUM([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded], '##0.0%;(##0.0%)'),
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Potential Bonus Tier'),
	IF([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded] >= 1.5,
    	'Tier 5',
        IF([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded] >= 1.3,
        	'Tier 4',
        	IF([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded] >= 1.2,
        		'Tier 3',
        		IF([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded] >= 1.05,
        			'Tier 2',
        			IF([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded] >= 1,
        				'Tier 1',
                        'N/A'
					)
				)
			)
		)
	),
            
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'),
	IF([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded] >= 1.5,
    	'50%',
        IF([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded] >= 1.3,
        	'30%',
        	IF([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded] >= 1.2,
        		'20%',
        		IF([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded] >= 1.05,
        			'10%',
        			IF([Bonusable NOI % - Nonexcluded] >= 1,
        				'2.5%',
                        'N/A'
					)
				)
			)
		)
	)
))))

=
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Quality Scores'),
	//FirstSortedValue({<FactType={'OneStream'}, Scenario={'Actual'}, AccountGroup={'CUSTSAT'}, Department={'None'}, Amount={">0"}, ExcludeBonusFlg-={'1'}>}  NUM(Amount*100, '##0') & ' ('  & IF(Month(%DateKey) <= 6, 'Mar', 'Sep')& Year(%DateKey) & ')', -%DateKey),
    //takes average scores
    NUM(AVG(AGGR(FirstSortedValue({<FactType={'OneStream'}, Scenario={'Actual'}, AccountGroup={'CUSTSAT'}, Department={'None'}, Amount={">0"}, ExcludeBonusFlg-={'1'}>}  Amount*100, -%DateKey), CampusName)),'##0')
	& ' '
	&
	//concats all periods from which those average scores are derived
    CONCAT(distinct AGGR(FirstSortedValue({<FactType={'OneStream'}, Scenario={'Actual'}, AccountGroup={'CUSTSAT'}, Department={'None'}, Amount={">0"}, ExcludeBonusFlg-={'1'}>}  ' ('  & IF(Month(%DateKey) <= 6, 'Mar', 'Sep')& Year(%DateKey) & ')', -%DateKey), CampusName)),
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), '% of NOI Target'),
	' ',
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Potential Bonus Tier'),
	' ',
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'),
	' '
))))

=
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Quality Scores'),
	//FirstSortedValue({<FactType={'OneStream'}, Scenario={'Actual'}, AccountGroup={'EMPLOYSAT'}, Department={'None'}, Amount={">0"}, ExcludeBonusFlg-={'1'}>} NUM(Amount*100, '##0') & ' ('  & IF(Month(%DateKey) <= 6, 'Mar', 'Sep')& Year(%DateKey) & ')', -%DateKey),
    //takes average scores
    NUM(AVG(AGGR(FirstSortedValue({<FactType={'OneStream'}, Scenario={'Actual'}, AccountGroup={'EMPLOYSAT'}, Department={'None'}, Amount={">0"}, ExcludeBonusFlg-={'1'}>}  Amount*100, -%DateKey), CampusName)),'##0')
	& ' '
	&
	//concats all periods from which those average scores are derived
    CONCAT(distinct AGGR(FirstSortedValue({<FactType={'OneStream'}, Scenario={'Actual'}, AccountGroup={'EMPLOYSAT'}, Department={'None'}, Amount={">0"}, ExcludeBonusFlg-={'1'}>}  ' ('  & IF(Month(%DateKey) <= 6, 'Mar', 'Sep')& Year(%DateKey) & ')', -%DateKey), CampusName)),    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), '% of NOI Target'),
	' ',
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Potential Bonus Tier'),
	' ',
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'),
	' '
))))

=
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Quality Scores'),
	//FirstSortedValue({<FactType={'OneStream'}, Scenario={'Actual'}, AccountGroup={'QASCORE'}, Department={'None'}, Amount={">0"}, ExcludeBonusFlg-={'1'}>} Amount*100 & ' (' & Year(%DateKey) & IF(Month(%DateKey) <= 6, 'R1', 'R2') & ')', -%DateKey),
    //takes average scores
    NUM(AVG(AGGR(AVG({<FactType={'QE'}, ExcludeBonusFlg-={'1'}>} [Net Score]), CampusName)),'##0')
	& ' '
	&
	//concats all periods from which those average scores are derived
    ' ('
    &
    CONCAT(distinct AGGR(MaxString({<FactType={'QE'}, ExcludeBonusFlg-={'1'}>}  IF(GetSelectedCount(OperationCluster)=1, CampusName & ' ', NULL()) & ReviewYearAndRound), CampusName), ' | ')
     &
     ')',    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), '% of NOI Target'),
	' ',
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Potential Bonus Tier'),
	' ',
    
IF(WildMatch(ValueList('Quality Scores', '% of NOI Target', 'Potential Bonus Tier', 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'), 'Potential Bonus Eligibility'),
	' '
))))

qCalcCond.qv:
= //one community selected or only access to one community and not a cluster
((GetSelectedCount(CampusName) = 1 or GetSelectedCount(CommunityName)=1 or GetPossibleCount(CampusName)=1) and GetPossibleCount(OperationCluster) = 0)
OR
//one cluster selected and none or all communities selected (to ensure you are seeing all communities in the cluster)
((GetSelectedCount(OperationCluster) = 1 ) and GetPossibleCount(OperationCluster) = 1 and (GetSelectedCount(CampusName) = 0 or GetSelectedCount(CampusName) = Count({<CampusName>}distinct CampusName)))
OR
//for cases when the community name selected is actually a campus (e.g., woodbriar, setauket, woodlands) which would cover all communities in the cluster/campus
(GetSelectedCount(CampusName) = 1 and MaxString(OperationCluster) = MaxString(CampusName))

qCond.qv:
= //one community selected or only access to one community and not a cluster
((GetSelectedCount(CampusName) = 1 or GetSelectedCount(CommunityName)=1 or GetPossibleCount(CampusName)=1) and GetPossibleCount(OperationCluster) = 0)
OR
//one cluster selected and none or all communities selected (to ensure you are seeing all communities in the cluster)
((GetSelectedCount(OperationCluster) = 1 ) and GetPossibleCount(OperationCluster) = 1 and (GetSelectedCount(CampusName) = 0 or GetSelectedCount(CampusName) = Count({<CampusName>}distinct CampusName)))
OR
//for cases when the community name selected is actually a campus (e.g., woodbriar, setauket, woodlands) which would cover all communities in the cluster/campus
(GetSelectedCount(CampusName) = 1 and MaxString(OperationCluster) = MaxString(CampusName))
